		"description": "Sample calls for the EAC Policy extension. Configure variables: AB_BASE_URL, AB_NAMESPACE, AB_CLIENT_ID, AB_CLIENT_SECRET, EXTEND_APP_SERVICE_URL, USER_ACCESS_TOKEN (user JWT), TEST_USER_ID.",
